Package org.opensextant.giscore.output.wkt

Class WKTOutputStream

java.lang.Object
org.opensextant.giscore.output.StreamVisitorBase
org.opensextant.giscore.output.wkt.WKTOutputStream
All Implemented Interfaces:
Closeable, AutoCloseable, IStreamVisitor, IGISOutputStream
public class WKTOutputStream extends StreamVisitorBase implements IGISOutputStream
Outputs an OGC Well-known text (WKT) format of a series of geometry objects. This only deals with WGS 84 right now.
Author:
DRAND
